				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: AGRO KITING - what bards were Made to do<a name="8519"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 25 03 12:32 PM</span></td>
