				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: AGRO KITING - what bards were Made to do<a name="8984"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 10 03 3:09 AM</span></td>
