				<td colspan="2"><span>Why bother agro kiting when you can swarm mobs for much more exp and dps then a full group or any of the combos above?  BTW the reason you can twist 5 dots is because the damage ticks over twice. Anywho this is how you swarm.
<br />

<br />
I use the Plane of Disease for swarming, what i do is agro 15-20 oozes and rats by running around them and pulling them to a mob free open safe area, after i have them all bunched up and chasing me, I charm one of the mobs to make it my pet then sick it on another mob in my swarm, all the mobs quickly turn on my pet and it only takes roughly 10 seconds for my pets hp to drop to around 10-15%, upon its massive hp loss i break charm with an invis item, and dot my previous pet till its dead and get exp for it (the dps is insane because pod mobs hit for 255-355 damage, but the mobs themselves have around 7-10k hps) anywho i make one yellow of exp every 30 minutes or so, and produce more dps than any group ive ever been with and get realy good exp!</span></td>
